.TP
.B \f[B]keygen\f[]
Generate Private Key with given parameters.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]key2pub\f[]
Extract Public Key from the Private Key.
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]encrypt\f[]
Encrypt data for given recipients which can be defined by Virgil Keys
and by passwords.
.RS
.RE
.TP
